data.description: Perfect Location with modern upgrades! Perfectly situated across the street from Smyrna High School and just a stone's throw from Nissan. With a spacious 2-car garage, and a beautifully updated kitchen, this home offers the perfect blend of comfort and convenience. This home offers a private retreat for outdoor activities and al fresco dining, making it an entertainer's delight. New HVAC installed June 2023, tankless water heater, fully fence back yard, electric fireplace stays. She shed with electric and HVAC.
